---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";

// URL base de WhatsApp para agilizar reservas
const waBase = "https://wa.me/51953618734?text=";
---

<Layout>
  <!-- Hero Section Integrado como Componente Extractor -->
  <Hero />

  <!-- Categorías / Trust Factors -->
  <section class="bg-blue-600 py-6">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div
        class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6 md:gap-12 text-center"
      >
        <p
          class="text-sm md:text-base font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-blue-100"
        >
          Equipamiento profesional en:
        </p>
        <div
          class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 md:gap-8 opacity-90 font-bold text-white text-lg sm:text-xl"
        >
          <span class="font-serif tracking-tighter">Sistemas de Audio</span>
          <span class="font-sans">Microfonía Inalámbrica</span>
          <span class="font-mono">Iluminación de Potencia</span>
          <span class="italic">Generadores Eléctricos</span>
          <span class="font-sans font-light">Estructuras Truss</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Ventajas Competitivas -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white border-b border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
        <!-- V1 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div
            class="flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 mb-6"
          >
            <svg
              class="h-8 w-8"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg
            >
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
            Equipos de Respaldo
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Llevamos unidades extra. Cero interrupciones garantizadas durante tu
            fiesta o presentación.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- V2 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div
            class="flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 mb-6"
          >
            <svg
              class="h-8 w-8"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
            >
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
            Instalación Estética
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Cero cables a la vista. Cuidamos el aspecto visual con encintado
            profesional, ideal para bodas.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- V3 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div
            class="flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 mb-6"
          >
            <svg
              class="h-8 w-8"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg
            >
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Cero Apagones</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Contamos con generadores propios insonorizados para que tu evento
            nunca se detenga ante fallas externas.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Combos Populares (La Máquina de Ventas) -->
  <section id="paquetes" class="py-20 bg-gray-50 scroll-mt-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Combos y Paquetes Populares
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Soluciones listas para sonar. Diseñadas estratégicamente para cubrir
          distintos tipos de eventos en Moquegua.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 items-start"
      >
        <!-- Card 1: Conferencias -->
        <article
          class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow"
        >
          <div class="p-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
              Paquete Conferencias
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">
              Sonido nítido para reuniones y charlas.
            </p>
            <div class="mb-6">
              <a
                href={`${waBase}Hola,%20quisiera%20cotizar%20el%20Paquete%20Conferencias`}
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="group flex items-center text-2xl font-extrabold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 transition-colors"
              >
                Cotizar paquete
                <svg
                  class="w-5 h-5 ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path></svg
                >
              </a>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg
                  class="h-6 w-6 text-green-500 shrink-0"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                >
                <span class="ml-3 text-gray-700"
                  >2 Parlantes Activos Alta Gama</span
                >
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg
                  class="h-6 w-6 text-green-500 shrink-0"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                >
                <span class="ml-3 text-gray-700"
                  >2 Micros UHF (Sin cables, anti-acople)</span
                >
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg
                  class="h-6 w-6 text-green-500 shrink-0"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                >
                <span class="ml-3 text-gray-700">Mixer analógico + Cables</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a
              href={`${waBase}Hola,%20quisiera%20cotizar%20el%20Paquete%20Conferencias`}
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="w-full inline-flex justify-center items-center px-4 py-3 border border-blue-600 shadow-sm text-base font-bold rounded-lg text-blue-700 bg-blue-50 hover:bg-blue-100 transition-colors"
            >
              Cotizar por WhatsApp
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Card 2: Combo Fiesta (Destacado) -->
        <article
          class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl border-2 border-blue-500 overflow-hidden transform md:-translate-y-4 relative z-10"
        >
          <div class="bg-blue-600 text-center py-2">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-white"
              >🔥 El Más Popular</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="p-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
              Combo Fiesta / DJ
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">
              Potencia y luces para bodas y cumpleaños.
            </p>
            <div class="mb-6">
              <a
                href={`${waBase}Hola,%20quisiera%20cotizar%20el%20Combo%20Fiesta%2FDJ`}
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="group flex items-center text-3xl font-extrabold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 transition-colors"
              >
                Cotizar combo
                <svg
                  class="w-6 h-6 ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path></svg
                >
              </a>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg
                  class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-500 shrink-0"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                >
                <span class="ml-3 text-gray-700 font-medium"
                  >Parlantes + Subwoofer</span
                >
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg
                  class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-500 shrink-0"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                >
                <span class="ml-3 text-gray-700">Set de Luces LED y Láser</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg
                  class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-500 shrink-0"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                >
                <span class="ml-3 text-gray-700"
                  >Estructura Truss en T (Luces)</span
                >
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg
                  class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-500 shrink-0"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                >
                <span class="ml-3 text-gray-700"
                  >Micrófonos + Controlador DJ</span
                >
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a
              href={`${waBase}Hola,%20quisiera%20cotizar%20el%20Combo%20Fiesta%2FDJ`}
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="w-full inline-flex justify-center items-center px-4 py-4 border border-transparent shadow-md text-base font-bold rounded-lg text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform"
            >
              Cotizar por WhatsApp
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Card 3: Especial Exterior (NUEVO GANCHOS) -->
        <article
          class="bg-gray-900 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-700 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-2xl transition-all group flex flex-col h-full"
        >
          <div
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 to-orange-600 text-center py-2"
          >
            <span
              class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-white"
              >⭐ Especial Exterior</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 flex-1 flex flex-col">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Exterior / Campo</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6">
              Energía y potencia donde sea.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 flex-1">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg
                  class="h-6 w-6 text-amber-500 shrink-0"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                >
                <span class="ml-3 text-gray-300"
                  ><strong>Generadores Eléctricos</strong></span
                >
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg
                  class="h-6 w-6 text-amber-500 shrink-0"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                >
                <span class="ml-3 text-gray-300">Reflectores LED</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg
                  class="h-6 w-6 text-amber-500 shrink-0"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                >
                <span class="ml-3 text-gray-300">Sonido + DJ + Montaje</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a
              href={`${waBase}Hola,%20quisiera%20cotizar%20el%20Especial%20Evento%20Exterior%20con%20Generador`}
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="w-full inline-flex justify-center items-center px-4 py-3 border border-amber-600 rounded-lg text-white bg-amber-600/20 font-bold hover:bg-amber-600 transition-colors"
            >
              Cotizar Especial
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Card 4: Concierto / Orquesta -->
        <article
          class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow"
        >
          <div class="p-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
              Paquete Concierto
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">
              Para bandas en vivo y orquestas grandes.
            </p>
            <div class="mb-6">
              <a
                href={`${waBase}Hola,%20quisiera%20cotizar%20el%20Paquete%20Concierto`}
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="group flex items-center text-2xl font-extrabold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 transition-colors"
              >
                Cotizar a medida
                <svg
                  class="w-5 h-5 ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path></svg
                >
              </a>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg
                  class="h-6 w-6 text-green-500 shrink-0"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                >
                <span class="ml-3 text-gray-700"
                  >Sistema Line Array + Monitores</span
                >
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg
                  class="h-6 w-6 text-green-500 shrink-0"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                >
                <span class="ml-3 text-gray-700"
                  >Microfonía de Batería e Inst.</span
                >
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg
                  class="h-6 w-6 text-green-500 shrink-0"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                >
                <span class="ml-3 text-gray-700"
                  >Consola Digital Inteligente (16+ Ch)</span
                >
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a
              href={`${waBase}Hola,%20quisiera%20cotizar%20el%20Paquete%20Concierto`}
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="w-full inline-flex justify-center items-center px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 shadow-sm text-base font-bold rounded-lg text-gray-700 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors"
            >
              Cotizar por WhatsApp
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section (HTML5 <details> y <summary>) -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Preguntas Frecuentes
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
          Resolvemos tus dudas de inmediato para que reserves con tranquilidad.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <!-- FAQ 1 -->
        <details
          class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 open:bg-white open:shadow-md transition-all"
        >
          <summary
            class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900 p-5 select-none focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 rounded-lg"
          >
            <h3>¿El precio incluye movilidad e instalación?</h3>
            <span
              class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180 flex-shrink-0 ml-4"
            >
              <svg
                fill="none"
                height="24"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg
              >
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div
            class="px-5 pb-5 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 pt-4 mt-1"
          >
            Sí, la movilidad e instalación están <strong
              >incluidas al 100%</strong
            > sin costos ocultos si tu evento se realiza dentro del área de Moquegua
            Cercado. Para zonas alejadas como Ilo, aplicará una tarifa justa de viáticos.
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- FAQ 2 -->
        <details
          class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 open:bg-white open:shadow-md transition-all"
        >
          <summary
            class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900 p-5 select-none focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 rounded-lg"
          >
            <h3>¿Cuánto tiempo antes arman los equipos?</h3>
            <span
              class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180 flex-shrink-0 ml-4"
            >
              <svg
                fill="none"
                height="24"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg
              >
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div
            class="px-5 pb-5 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 pt-4 mt-1"
          >
            Llegamos e instalamos por lo menos <strong>2 horas antes</strong> de tu
            evento. Queremos que el sonido esté equilibrado, los cables escondidos
            estéticamente y las pruebas de micrófono completas antes de que llegue
            el primer invitado.
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- FAQ 3 -->
        <details
          class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 open:bg-white open:shadow-md transition-all"
        >
          <summary
            class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900 p-5 select-none focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 rounded-lg"
          >
            <h3>¿Qué pasa si un equipo falla durante la fiesta?</h3>
            <span
              class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180 flex-shrink-0 ml-4"
            >
              <svg
                fill="none"
                height="24"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg
              >
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div
            class="px-5 pb-5 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 pt-4 mt-1"
          >
            Contamos con política de <strong>Equipos de Respaldo</strong>.
            Siempre llevamos micrófonos o cables extra (y canales de emergencia
            en consola) para sustituir de inmediato cualquier imprevisto sin
            interrumpir la celebración.
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- FAQ 4 -->
        <details
          class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 open:bg-white open:shadow-md transition-all"
        >
          <summary
            class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900 p-5 select-none focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 rounded-lg"
          >
            <h3>¿Necesito corriente especial o trifásica?</h3>
            <span
              class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180 flex-shrink-0 ml-4"
            >
              <svg
                fill="none"
                height="24"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg
              >
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div
            class="px-5 pb-5 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 pt-4 mt-1"
          >
            Nuestros paquetes Estándar y Fiesta operan perfectamente con <strong
              >tomacorrientes convencionales (220V)</strong
            >. Para el Paquete Orquesta sí se realizará una revisión previa del
            local y sus llaves de fuerza.
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- FAQ 5 -->
        <details
          class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 open:bg-white open:shadow-md transition-all"
        >
          <summary
            class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900 p-5 select-none focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 rounded-lg"
          >
            <h3>¿Puedo conectar mi propio Spotify/Laptop o llevar a mi DJ?</h3>
            <span
              class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180 flex-shrink-0 ml-4"
            >
              <svg
                fill="none"
                height="24"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg
              >
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div
            class="px-5 pb-5 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 pt-4 mt-1"
          >
            <strong>Totalmente.</strong> Facilitamos integración vía Bluetooth o cables
            (Jack 3.5mm/RCA) para conectar celulares y laptops. Si traes a tu propio
            DJ, el técnico simplemente conectará su controlador a nuestro sistema
            principal y monitoreará los niveles y ecualización.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
